like head start which is designed to help the early education of 
poor children and taking mental patients and throwing them into 
the street 
it means cutting down on police forces school lunches make it 
tough for handicapped to apply for social security taxing the 
elderly for medicare said etzioni above all it means using 
social security to cover deficits 
averting such an economic crisis he said may require a major 
change that would allow the us economy to grow at a faster pace 
but he said he doesnt believe the political parties have shown 
the willingness to deal with such a tough issue 
