the 10page speech was published monday in novy mir the nations 
leading literary journal solzhenitsyn wrote it after winning the 
nobel prize for literature in 1970 
soviet officials barred him from traveling to sweden to give the 
lecture 
publication of the nobel speech marked another important step 
toward the rehabilitation of solzhenitsyn who was kicked out of the 
soviet writers union in 1969 and exiled to the west five years 
