administration budget cuts 
both are true revenue experts can talk for hours about how 
changes in the federal tax code the stock market crash of october 
1987 and this years sales tax decline made a mockery of their 
revenue estimates the numbers on which state spending is planned 
but critics who hold a more conservative fiscal viewpoint than 
dukakis say the governor and the legislature over the past six years 
simply allowed state spending to rise out of control 
