pressure from the legislature and public opinion repealed a surtax 
he had imposed in his first term the move cut state revenue by 280 
million other tax cuts which dukakis eventually supported trimmed 
revenue by some 400 million during the past six years ironically 
those cuts just about equal the shortfall the state is facing 
