in yellow black and red colors of the united democratic front 
south africas main antiapartheid alliance before it was banned 
last year 
a son held up a fruit basket with ribbons in green black and 
yellow colors of the outlawed anc guerrilla movement 
about 20 supporters of mandela shouted viva anc and viva 
mandela as relatives arrived in five cars at the gates of the 
prison farm mandela was transferred there from a cape town prison 
after he recovered from tuberculosis last year 
wellwishers stood in the rain in nearfreezing temperatures on 
one of the coldest days in recent years 
mandela has been in prison since 1962 and he is serving a life 
term for sabotage and plotting to overthrow the white government 
