the people from montana and wyoming want to know what its 
about and i try to explain it to them but then they usually dont 
want to have anything to do with it they say give me a cup of 
coffee 
originally a middle eastern drink espresso was transported to 
italy and from there all over the world todays version is brewed 
in a special machine where 200degree water is pressured through 
darkroasted coffee beans that have been ground to a dustlike 
consistency 
the result is a concentrated syrupy brew that can cost from 70 
cents to 2 or more for an exotic drink 
