vice president dan quayle said tuesday the 
united states should commit itself to exploring and developing space 
and that congress should fully fund construction of a manned space 
station 
the president and i are committed to american leadership in 
exploration understanding economic use and yes eventual 
settlement in space he said in an address to 4000 employees of 
